@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram - Weather Station System

[*] --> Running

state "Running" as Running
state "Configuration" as Configuration
state "Controlled" as Controlled
state "Shutdown" as Shutdown

Running : entry / Collect data, prepare summary, check status
Running : do / Perform activities
Running : exit / Return to Running state

Running --> Configuration : [Changes or power-saving settings required]
Running --> Controlled : [Remote control command received]
Running --> Shutdown : [Shutdown command received]

Configuration : entry / Configure system
Configuration : do / Apply changes, save settings
Configuration : exit / Return to Running state

Controlled : entry / Awaiting remote control commands
Controlled : do / Perform activities based on commands
Controlled : exit / Return to Running state

Shutdown : entry / Shut down system
Shutdown : do / Save data, power off
Shutdown : exit / [*]

Running --> Running : [Activity completed]
Configuration --> Configuration : [Configuration completed]
Controlled --> Controlled : [Remote control command received]
Shutdown --> Shutdown : [System shutdown]
@enduml
